==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lachrymal
<hw>Lach"ry*mal</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>lacrymal</ets>. See <er>Lachrymose</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of
or pertaining to tears; <as>as, <ex>lachrymal</ex>
effusions</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or secreting,
tears; <as>as, the <ex>lachrymal</ex> gland</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to the lachrymal{2}
organs; <as>as, <ex>lachrymal</ex> bone; <ex>lachrymal</ex>
duct.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lacrymal</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Lachrymal</ent>⟦br⟧
